      "writtenOn": "2020-08-11T08:11:20Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "chromiumos/tast/ssh is a package imported from both the framework and Tast tests. But we don\u0027t plan to provide the config parser to Tast tests --- providing something to Tast tests means that we have to maintain its API compatibility, so we don\u0027t want to bother to do so until it becomes really needed.\n\nSo, can you move the config parser to chromiumos/tast/internal/sshconfig? Packages under chromiumos/tast/internal are private to the framework and can\u0027t be imported from Tast tests.",
      "revId": "e85101a7ba03dc19e80dee75109a27f964fad4e6",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
